# Jobfynder Brand OS

Single source of truth for Jobfynder's brand. Built on Stephen Houraghan's 12-Pillar Brand OS framework.

"Brands that make it start small, but structured. They define what matters and what doesn't, and then work inside those limits. That structure becomes friction, grip in the market, and that grip builds traction."

## The Canon

| Element | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Tagline | Connect with Clarity |
| Product Line | Connect. Submit. Place. |
| One-Liner | Jobfynder is the Professional Network Built for US Staffing — where relationships are verified, submissions are tracked, and placements accelerate. |
| Internal Line | Turn recruiting chaos into trusted outcomes. |
